            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>meat-free burger patty[ies]</strong>, <strong>grated ginger </strong>and <strong>sliced spring onion </strong>to a bowl with 1 tsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tsp] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tsp]</span> <strong>sugar</strong> and a grind of <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Using clean hands, give everything a very good mix up until fully combined – this is your<strong> meat-free burger mixture</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
