    {
      "instruction": "<p>Divide the<strong> meat-free burger mixture </strong>equally and shape into 1 patty per person</p><p>Sprinkle the <strong>toasted sesame seeds</strong> evenly over the burger patty[ies]</p><p>Lightly oil a baking tray with <strong>vegetable oil</strong> and add the <strong>sesame meat-free burger patty[ies]</strong>,<strong> </strong>put the tray in the oven for 10-12 min or until cooked through</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1615910509619-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1615910509619-x400.jpg",
