            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, combine <strong>half</strong> of your <strong>sriracha </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!), <strong>rice vinegar</strong> and a pinch of <strong>sugar</strong> and <strong>salt</strong> in a bowl</p><p>Top, tail, peel and grate your <strong>carrot[s]</strong></p><p>Peel lengths off the <strong>cucumber</strong> until you end up with a pile of cucumber ribbons</p><p>Add the <strong>grated carrot</strong> and <strong>cucumber ribbons</strong> to the bowl, give everything a good mix up and set aside – this is your <strong>quick-pickled slaw</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1615910515395-x200.jpg",
