            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine your <strong>mayo</strong> and <strong>remaining sriracha</strong> (not a fan of spice? Just add a little!) in a bowl – this is your<strong> sriracha mayo</strong></p><p>Chop your <strong>coriander</strong> roughly, including the stalks</p><p>Drain the <strong>quick-pickled slaw</strong> of any excess pickling liquid, discard the liquid</p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
