            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>To assemble, spread a<strong> toasted brioche base</strong> with some <strong>sriracha mayo</strong>, then top with a <strong>sesame meat-free burger patty</strong>, <strong>quick-pickled slaw</strong> and another dollop of <strong>sriracha mayo</strong> and a<strong> toasted brioche lid </strong>– this is your<strong> sesame meat-free burger</strong></p><p>Serve the <strong>chips</strong> and any <strong>remaining quick-pickled slaw</strong> to the side and sprinkle over the <strong>chopped coriander</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
      "order": 8,
